messages.message: Hey team, do we have a Postman collection for making API calls to deployments? From what I can see its a different endpoint to running a standalone app
The reason I ask is I am doing a demo on API calls for deployed prod use cases, so if not I'll need to put something together myself from the auto-generated code :slightly_smiling_face:
We do not yet - @tony.shi and @Adam, is this something that would be quick to put together?

While I donâ€™t think it would be too hard to add to postman, are we also planning on adding deployment runs to our sdk? I think we should probably get a complete picture of the API consumption plan before we do it partially
We should have API parity for deployments as we do for apps as this is the primary way we expect users to drive account consumption.
